ng%20and%20private%20messaging.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20could%20argue%20that%20Instagram%20is%20a%20social%20media%20network%20like%20no%20other.%20The%20popular%20user%20base%20platform%20is%20built%20almost%20entirely%20around%20sharing%20images%20and%20videos.%20This%20visual%20twist%20is%20why%20Instagram%20is%20the%20cultural%20powerhouse%20it%20is%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20over%20a%20billion%20registered%20accounts%2C%20from%20small%20businesses%20to%20large%20institutions%2C%20news%20organizations%20to%20cultural%20hubs%2C%20celebrities%2C%20photographers%2C%20musicians%2C%20and%20not%20to%20mention%20the%20cottage%20industry%20of%20influencers%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20hard%20to%20remember%20a%20time%20when%20Instagram%20didn't%20exist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20if%20you've%20found%20yourself%20out%20of%20the%20Instagram%20loop%2C%20then%20read%20on.%20We'll%20give%20you%20a%20crash%20course%20on%20how%20the%20app%20works%2C%20how%20to%20get%20started%2C%20and%20eventually%2C%20how%20to%20get%20'gramming%20like%20a%20pro.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20sign%20up%20for%20Instagram%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20help%20you%20get%20started%2C%20let's%20walk%20through%20some%20of%20the%20basics%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20download%20Instagram%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%20things%20first%3A%20You'll%20need%20to%20download%20Instagram%20to%20use%20the%20app.%20It's%20available%20for%20free%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Finstagram%2Fid389801252%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EiOS%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.instagram.android%26hl%3Den_US%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAndroid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D18d5fb2305e07033db8398b