%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22686%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Screenshot%20shows%20a%20list%20of%20notifications%20on%20the%20Instagram%20app%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65086bc4cd637c0019c6f736%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221204%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20you%20have%20the%20app%20downloaded%2C%20and%20your%20profile%20set%20up%2C%20it's%20time%20to%20start%20sharing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20use%20Instagram%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20its%20core%2C%20Instagram%20is%20a%20social%20media%20platform%2C%20and%20a%20highly%20visual%20one%20at%20that.%20Every%20time%20you%20open%20the%20app%2C%20you'll%20be%20met%20with%20a%20main%20feed%20of%20recent%20posts%20from%20the%20accounts%20you%20follow.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20bottom%20is%20a%20menu%20bar%2C%20which%20is%20accessible%20anywhere%20you%20are%20in%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20each%20button%20does%2C%20from%20left%20to%20right%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22708%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20of%20the%20Instagram%20app%20on%20a%20mobile%20iOS%20device%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650867e2cd637c0019c6f198%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221232%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUse%20these%20buttons%20to%20navigate%20between%20your%20feed%2C%20search%20and%20Explore%2C%20new%20post%2C%20Reels%2C%20and%20your%20profile.%3Cp%3EInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHome%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Your%20main%20feed%20where%20you%20can%20scroll%20through%20photos%20and%20videos%20posted%20by%20your%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESearch%20and%20explore%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20magnifying%20glass%20icon%20takes%20you%20to%20the%20Explore%20page%2C%20where%20you%20can%20search%20and%20browse%20content%20from%20accounts%20you%20don't%20follow%20but%20may%20be%20interested%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20post%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20%26quot%3Bplus%26quot%3B%20icon%20allows%20you%20to%20create%20a%20new%20story%2C%20post%2C%20Reel%2C%20or%20Instagram%20Live.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReels%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20This%20tab%20includes%20short%20videos%20(up%20to%2090%20seconds%20long)%20from%20users%20you%20may%20or%20may%20not%20be%20following.%20You%20can%20scroll%20to%20the%20next%20video%20by%20swiping%20your%20finger%20from%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20screen%20to%20the%20top.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProfile%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20This%20icon%20navigates%20to%20your%20profile%20page%20that%20shows%20your%20bio%20and%20posts.%20It's%20also%20where%20you%20can%20access%20your%20settings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20other%20social%20media%20networks%2C%20Instagram%20is%20what%20you%20make%20it.%20For%20most%20people%2C%20checking%20Instagram%20is%20equal%20parts%20voyeurism%20and%20self-expression.%20For%20the%20entrepreneurial%20set%2C%20like%20business%20owners%2C%20brands%2C%20and%20influencers%2C%20Instagram%20is%20an%20indispensable%20marketing%20tool%20with%20unmatched%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20going%20back%20to%20basics%2C%20Instagram%20works%20off%20a%20simple%20premise%3A%20You%20follow%20accounts%20that%20interest%20you.%20In%20turn%2C%20people%20follow%20you.%20Much%20like%20on%20Instagram's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-apps%5C%22%3EMeta%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%20sibling%20Facebook%2C%20people%20can%20%26quot%3Blike%26quot%3B%20and%20comment%20on%20your%20posts%2C%20and%20you%20can%20do%20the%20same%20to%20their%20posts.%20Whether%20you%20maintain%20a%20low%20profile%20or%20amass%20a%20following%2C%20how%20active%20you%20are%20is%20entirely%20up%20to%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EUploading%2C%20editing%2C%20and%20posting%20photos%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20share%20a%20photo%20or%20video%20on%20Instagram%2C%20tap%20the%20plus%20button%20(located%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20screen).%20From%20there%2C%20you%20can%20select%20photos%20or%20videos%20from%20your%20phone's%20camera%20roll%20to%20post.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20every%20post%2C%20you%20can%20choose%20to%20apply%20a%20filter%2C%20which%2C%20depending%20on%20who%20you%20ask%2C%20is%20either%20essential%20to%20the%20Instagram%20experience%20or%20unnecessary%2C%20given%20that%20many%20other%20photo%20editing%20apps%20come%20with%20their%20own%20filters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFilters%20make%20it%20easy%20to%20edit%20shots%20with%20different%20visual%20pre-set%20overlays.%20For%20example%2C%20some%20filters%2C%20like%20Mayfair%2C%20give%20everything%20a%20pink%20hue%3B%20others%2C%20like%20Willow%2C%20turn%20everything%20black-and-white.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20adjust%20how%20intense%20(or%20not)%20the%20filter%20is%20as%20well%20using%20a%20slider%20when%20you%20select%20the%20filter%20and%20then%20tap%20it%20one%20more%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22688%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20of%20what%20it%20looks%20like%20to%20post%20a%20story%20on%20the%20Instagram%20app%20on%20a%20mobile%20iOS%20device%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65086871cd637c0019c6f25e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221242%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20options%20in%20Instagram's%20posting%20screen.%3Cp%3EInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20your%20post%20is%20to%20your%20liking%20and%20ready%20to%20go%2C%20there%20are%20a%20few%20more%20options%20you%20can%20do%20before%20you%20hit%20the%20share%20button%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdd%20a%20caption%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Captions%20are%20always%20a%20good%20idea.%20You%20can%20use%20words%2C%20emojis%2C%20or%20hashtags.%20Just%20like%20in%20comments%2C%20you%20can%20also%20%3Cem%3Emention%3C%2Fem%3E%20friends%20by%20typing%20%40%20in%20front%20of%20their%20username.%20Keep%20in%20mind%20you%20can%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-edit-instagram-post%5C%22%3Eedit%20Instagram%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20captions%20at%20any%20time%20%E2%80%94%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-delete-instagram-post%5C%22%3Edelete%20posts%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETag%20people%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Instagram%20allows%20you%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-tag-someone-on-instagram%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Btag%26quot%3B%20someone%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20your%20photos.%20When%20you%20tag%20someone%2C%20they'll%20get%20a%20notification%20in%20their%20activity%20feed.%20(This%20is%20separate%20from%20mentioning%20them%20in%20your%20caption.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdd%20location%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Location%20tags%20lets%20others%20know%20where%20your%20photo%20was%20taken.%20Clicking%20on%20a%20location%20tag%20brings%20you%20to%20its%20corresponding%20location%20feed%2C%20where%20you%20can%20peruse%20other%20public%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20post%20to%20other%20social%20accounts%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Instagram%20also%20gives%20you%20the%20ability%20to%20publish%20a%20post%20to%20other%20social%20accounts%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20By%20linking%20accounts%2C%20you%20can%20cross-post%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-claim-725-million-facebook-settlement-2023-4%5C%22%3EFacebook%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20X%20(formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter)%2C%20and%20Tumblr.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EExploring%20and%20finding%20people%20to%20follow%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20way%20to%20find%20people%20to%20follow%20is%20by%20tapping%20the%20magnifying%20glass%20icon%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20app.%20This%20will%20open%20the%20Explore%20page%2C%20where%20you'll%20find%20a%20feed%20of%20suggested%20posts%20based%20on%20what%20Instagram%20thinks%20you're%20interested%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22702%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20of%20Instagram%E2%80%99s%20Explore%20tab%20on%20mobile%20iOS.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650868c4f05aa00019be3caa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221198%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20can%20scroll%20down%20for%20more%20posts%2C%20or%20use%20the%20search%20function%20at%20the%20top%20to%20find%20specific%20accounts%20or%20posts.%3Cp%3EInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cbr%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20interacting%20with%20others%2C%20Instagram%20works%20less%20like%20Facebook%20and%20more%20like%20Twitter.%20In%20most%20cases%2C%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20send%20a%20friend%20request%20or%20wait%20for%20the%20other%20person%20to%20accept%20it.%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20follow%20other%20people%2C%20Instagram%20will%20make%20sure%20you%20see%20their%20posts%20in%20your%20feed.%20For%20the%20most%20part%2C%20people%20can%20see%20who%20you're%20following%20and%20who's%20following%20you%2C%20at%20all%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20if%20you%20have%20a%20private%20account%20your%20followers%20are%20restricted%20and%20unable%20to%20view%20who%20currently%20follows%20you.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESending%20and%20receiving%20direct%20messages%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-message-someone-on-instagram%5C%22%3EInstagram's%20direct%20messaging%3C%2Fa%3E%20system%20lets%20you%20chat%20privately%20with%20anyone%20who%20follows%20you.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20send%20a%20message%20to%20someone%20who%20doesn't%20follow%20you%2C%20that%20message%20will%20be%20sorted%20into%20its%20own%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-see-message-requests-on-instagram%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bmessage%20requests%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20folder.%20To%20start%20the%20conversation%2C%20the%20person%20on%20the%20receiving%20end%20must%20accept%20the%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDirect%20messages%20are%20also%20available%20in%20the%20app%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-dm-on-instagram-from-computer%5C%22%3Eand%20on%20the%20desktop%20website%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221166%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Instagram%20direct%20message%20inbox%20on%20mobile%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65086c59f05aa00019be41ac%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22874%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3ETo%20access%20your%20message%20menu%2C%20tap%20the%20paper%20airplane%20icon%20in%20your%20home%20feed.%20From%20there%2C%20you'll%20be%20shown%20all%20the%20people%20you've%20had%20conversations%20with%20in%20the%20past.%20You%20can%20also%20tap%20the%20pen%20and%20paper%20icon%20in%20the%20top%20right-hand%20corner%20to%20start%20a%20new%20conversation%2C%20or%20the%20camera%20icon%20to%20start%20a%20video%20chat.%3Cp%3EOnce%20you're%20in%20a%20conversation%2C%20you%20can%20send%20all%20sorts%20of%20messages.%20These%20include%20basic%20text%20messages%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-send-gifs-on-instagram-dm%5C%22%3Eanimated%20GIFs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20more.%20You%20can%20also%20share%20Instagram%20posts.%20And%20you%20can%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-like-messages-on-instagram%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Blike%26quot%3B%20messages%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-delete-instagram-messages%5C%22%3Edelete%20messages%20if%20you%20no%20longer%20wish%20to%20see%20them%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20users%20that%20you'll%20have%20to%20ask%20to%20follow%20are%20those%20who%20have%20made%20their%20account%20private.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20tap%20Follow%20on%20a%20private%20profile%2C%20you'll%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20that%20user%20to%20accept%20you%20before%20you%20can%20officially%20follow%20them%20and%20send%20them%20a%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-find-contacts-on-instagram%5C%22%3Econnect%20your%20phone%20contacts%20to%20Instagram%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20can%20be%20another%20great%20way%20to%20find%20friends%20on%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EInstagram%20features%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20you%20might%20expect%2C%20Instagram%20rolls%20out%20new%20features%20regularly.%20From%20new%20content%20to%20an%20ever-expanding%20set%20of%20creative%20tools%2C%20Instagram%20offers%20plenty%20of%20opportunities%20for%20self-expression%20and%20creativity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20latest%20and%20greatest%20Instagram%20features%20worth%20knowing%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EInstagram%20Stories%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20people%20use%20Instagram%20exclusively%20for%20creating%20and%20viewing%20Stories%2C%20which%20are%20customizable%20posts%20that%20only%20last%2024%20hours.%20These%20posts%2C%20which%20could%20be%20a%20mix%20of%20photos%20and%20short-form%20videos%2C%20are%20presented%20in%20a%20slideshow%20format%20and%20accessible%20through%20the%20top%20of%20the%20home%20feed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20when%20we%20say%20customizable%2C%20we%20mean%20customizable.%20Unlike%20regular%20posts%2C%20which%20include%20only%20simple%20filters%2C%20Stories%20boast%20all%20kinds%20of%20creative%20elements%2C%20including%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-add-stickers-on-instagram%5C%22%3EAnimated%20stickers%20and%20cartoons%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-make-a-poll-on-instagram%5C%22%3EPolls%20and%20quizzes%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-put-lyrics-on-instagram-story%5C%22%3EDynamic%20song%20lyrics%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-set-up-donation-on-instagram%5C%22%3ELinks%20to%20donation%20funds%20and%20charities%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20several%20ways%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-add-to-your-story-on-instagram%5C%22%3Eadd%20to%20your%20Story%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20the%20easiest%20is%20to%20tap%20your%20profile%20icon%20at%20the%20top-left%20hand%20corner%20of%20your%20home%20feed.%20From%20there%2C%20you%20can%20either%20take%20a%20photo%20or%20video%20live%2C%20or%20choose%20one%20from%20your%20phone's%20gallery.%20You'll%20then%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20draw%2C%20add%20text%20or%20any%20of%20those%20other%20creative%20elements%20we%20mentioned%20above.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Stories%20are%20designed%20to%20disappear%20after%20one%20day%2C%20they're%20automatically%20saved%20to%20your%20private%20Archive%20(which%20we'll%20explain%20in%20just%20a%20bit)%20after%20expiring.%20You%20can%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-add-suggested-highlight-on-instagram%5C%22%3Ecreate%20a%20Highlight%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20will%20publish%20Stories%20permanently%20on%20your%20profile%20for%20visitors%20to%20watch%20at%20any%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EInstagram%20Live%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EInstagram%20Live%20is%20a%20feature%20that%20lets%20you%20livestream%2C%20or%20broadcast%20live%20video%2C%20from%20your%20device%20to%20anyone%20who%20wants%20to%20watch.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EViewers%20can%20send%20you%20messages%20and%20hearts%20while%20you%20stream%2C%20making%20this%20a%20great%20way%20to%20talk%20to%20all%20your%20followers%20at%20once%2C%20or%20broadcast%20an%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20go%20live%20on%20Instagram%2C%20you'll%20need%20to%20open%20Instagram%20and%2C%20from%20your%20feed%2C%20swipe%20right%20and%20select%20Live%20from%20the%20options%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20screen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20go%20live%20for%20up%20to%20four%20hours%20at%20a%20time%20%E2%80%94%20after%20that%2C%20the%20livestream%20will%20end%20and%20you'll%20need%20to%20start%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EReels%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EBuilt%20as%20a%20rival%20to%20TikTok%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstagram-reels-tiktok-competitor-short-video-us-launch-explainer-2020-7%5C%22%3EReels%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20Instagram's%20dedicated%20video%20platform%2C%20letting%20users%20upload%20videos%20up%20to%2090%20seconds%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20you%20record%20a%20video%2C%20you%20can%20edit%20it%20and%20add%20music%2C%20text%2C%20and%20special%20effects.%20Other%20users%20can%20like%20or%20comment%20on%20your%20Reels%20videos%2C%20so%20they%20can%20be%20a%20fun%20way%20to%20attract%20new%20followers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20watch%20someones%20else's%20Reels%2C%20you%20need%20to%20tap%20the%20icon%2C%20located%20in%20the%20center%20of%20the%20bottom%20menu%20on%20the%20app.%20(It%20looks%20like%20a%20mashup%20of%20a%20play%20button%20and%20a%20clapperboard.)%20Here%2C%20you%20can%20watch%20videos%20that%20others%20have%20uploaded%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fhow-to-make-instagram-reels%5C%22%3Emake%20Reels%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0of%20your%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EInstagram%20Shopping%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20Instagram's%20popularity%2C%20it's%20no%20surprise%20that%20brands%20are%20doing%20everything%20they%20can%20to%20turn%20Instagram%20users%20into%20customers.%20According%20to%20Instagram%2C%20nearly%20half%20of%20people%20shop%20on%20Instagram%20weekly.%20Instagram%20Shopping%20is%20one%20way%20to%20use%20Instagram%20for%20your%20business%20by%20connecting%20potential%20customers%20to%20your%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EInstagram%20tips%20and%20tricks%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInstagram%20is%20simple%20to%20use%2C%20but%20can%20take%20a%20while%20to%20master.%20Here%20are%20some%20of%20our%20favorite%20tricks%20that%20aren't%20so%20obvious%20to%20beginners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3ESchedule%20posts%20in%20advance%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EInstagram%20has%20become%20a%20massive%20part%20of%20nearly%20every%20company's%20online%20presence%2C%20and%20if%20there's%20one%20thing%20that%20social%20media%20brand%20managers%20love%2C%20it's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-schedule-instagram-posts%5C%22%3Escheduling%20a%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstagram%20does%20have%20a%20native%20post%20scheduler%20%E2%80%94%20but%20that's%20reserved%20for%20those%20with%20professional%20accounts.%20Still%2C%20there%20are%20dozens%20of%20third-party%20programs%2C%20like%20Buffer%2C%20that%20can%20handle%20the%20scheduling%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3ESave%20Instagram%20videos%20to%20your%20phone%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you've%20found%20an%20amazing%20video%20on%20Instagram%20that%20you%20just%20need%20to%20save%2C%20you're%20in%20luck%20%E2%80%94%20there%20are%20several%20ways%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-save-instagram-videos%5C%22%3Esave%20Instagram%20videos%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20trying%20to%20save%20one%20of%20your%20own%20videos%2C%20it'll%20just%20take%20a%20few%20taps%20to%20save%20the%20video%20directly%20to%20your%20camera%20roll.%20If%20you're%20trying%20to%20save%20someone%20else's%20video%2C%20however%2C%20you'll%20need%20to%20record%20your%20screen%20or%20use%20a%20third-party%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EPost%20different%20photo%20formats%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Instagram%20first%20launched%20in%202010%2C%20the%20edits%20were%20limited.%20You%20could%20only%20post%20square%20photos%20%E2%80%94%20anything%20else%20either%20wasn't%20allowed%2C%20or%20would%20be%20cut%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENowadays%2C%20the%20rules%20are%20a%20bit%20more%20lax.%20But%20if%20you%20want%20to%20post%20two%20c