ith%20evidence%20against%20them%20but%20no%20action%20was%20taken%20by%20the%20Canadian%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20separatist%20organisation%20were%20openly%20issuing%20assassination%20threats%2C%20fuelling%20separatist%20agenda%20and%20carrying%20out%20targeted%20killings%20in%20India%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20pointed%20out%20that%20high-profile%20assassination%20of%20popular%20singer%20Sidhu%20Moose%20Wala%20by%20the%20Canada-based%20gangster%20with%20affiliations%20to%20pro-Khalistan%20elements%20%26quot%3Bis%20a%20classic%20example%20of%20this%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOther%20Canada-based%20wanted%20terrorists%20are%20Gurwant%20Singh%20Bath%20of%20the%20Dashmesh%20regiment%20of%20Khalistan%2C%20Bhagat%20Singh%20Brar%20(who%20is%20son%20of%20Pakistan-based%20terrorist%20Lakhbeer%20Singh%20Rhode)%2C%20Moninder%20Singh%20Bual%2C%20Satinder%20Pal%20Singh%20Gill%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENijjar%2C%20who%20carried%20a%20cash%20reward%20of%20Rs%2010%20lakh%2C%20was%20born%20in%20Punjab%20on%20November%2010%2C%201977%20and%20was%20affiliated%20with%20the%20now%20banned%20Khalistan%20Tiger%20Force%20(KTF).%20He%20was%20arrested%20in%20the%20mid%201990s.%20He%20managed%20to%20get%20bail%20and%20fled%20India%20on%20February%2019%2C%201997%20by%20assuming%20a%20fake%20identity%20of%20Ravi%20Sharma%20and%20securing%20a%20travel%20document%20in%20that%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202013-14%2C%20Nijjar%20visited%20Pakistan%20where%20he%20met%20Jagtar%20Singh%20Tara%20of%20Khalistan%20Tiger%20Force%20(KTF)%2C%20wanted%20in%20assassination%20of%20Punjab%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Beant%20Singh.%20He%20was%20during%20that%20period%20roped%20in%20by%20the%20ISI%20which%20helped%20him%20in%20organising%20secret%20training%20camps%20for%20Sikh%20extremist%20groups%20associated%20with%20the%20Khalistan%20movement%20in%20Missigen%20Hills%2C%20British%20Columbia.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENijjar%2C%20who%20was%20designated%20as%20a%20terrorist%20by%20the%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%2C%20was%20also%20accused%20of%20working%20closely%20with%20Babbar%20Khalsa%20International%20(BKI)%20led%20by%20Jagtar%20Singh%20Tara.%20He%20has%20been%20associated%20with%20Dal%20Khalsa%20leader%20Gajender%20Singh%2C%20a%20key%20accused%20in%20hijacking%20of%20an%20Indian%20Airlines%20flight%20in%201981.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20name%20figured%20in%20the%20most%20wanted%20list%20handed%20over%20by%20then%20Punjab%20Chief%20Minister%20Captain%20Amrinder%20Singh%20to%20the%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENijjar%20along%20with%20criminals%20like%20Arsh%20Dalla%20were%20generating%20huge%20amounts%20of%20funds%20for%20anti-India%20activities%20by%20various%20means%20which%20included%20drug%20money%20and%20finances%20from%20Gurdwaras%2C%20the%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20Canada's%20current%20diplomatic%20standoff%20with%20India%20appears%20to%20be%20motivated%20by%20failures%20on%20the%20domestic%20political%20front%20and%20declining%20popularity%20of%20the%20present%20government%20and%20expulsion%20of%20an%20Indian%20diplomat%20seems%20to%20be%20aimed%20at%20getting%20support%20of%20the%20Sikh%20population%20especially%20those%20harbouring%20pro-Khalistan%20sentiments.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20officials%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20support%20for%20extremist%20elements%20and%20gangsters%20in%20Canada%20are%20deeply%20linked%20with%20the%20political%20realities%20that%20influence%20the%20vote%20bank%20in%20various%20Sikh%20dominated%20constituencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20pointed%20to%20the%20role%20of%20Jagmeet%20Singh%20Dhaliwal%2C%20an%20MP%20from%20Burnaby%20South%2C%20who%20belongs%20to%20the%20New%20Democratic%20Party%20of%20Canada%20which%20has%20been%20a%20vocal%20supporter%20of%20the%20Khalistan%20referendum%20that%20seeks%20a%20Balkanisation%20of%20India%20and%20fuels%20separatist%20sentiments%20amongst%20Canadian%20Sikhs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ED