ratory%20studies%20on%20the%20two%20alleged%20%26quot%3Bnon-human%26quot%3B%20alien%20corpses%20revealed%20last%20week.%20The%20tests%20were%20carried%20out%20by%20Jose%20de%20Jesus%20Zalce%20Benitez%2C%20a%20forensic%20doctor%20with%20the%20navy%20at%20the%20Noor%20Clinic%20on%20Monday%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-66853551%5C%22%3EBBC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr.%20Benitez%20concluded%20that%20the%20so-called%20bodies%20belonged%20to%20a%20single%20skeleton%20and%20were%20not%20assembled.%20He%C2%A0also%20said%20that%20the%20laboratory%20tests%20have%20shown%20that%20''there%20is%20no%20evidence%20of%20any%20assembly%20or%20manipulation%20of%20the%20skulls''.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fwatch-mysterious-non-human-alien-corpses-displayed-at-mexicos-congress-4386001%5C%22%3E%20mummies%20were%20presented%20by%20Jaime%20Maussan%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20journalist%20who%20has%20speculated%20widely%20on%20aliens.%20The%20mysterious%20bodies%20are%20tiny%20in%20stature%20and%20chalky%20in%20colour%2C%20and%20each%20one%20of%20them%20has%20three-fingered%20hands%20and%20shrunken%20heads.%C2%A0One%20was%20described%20as%20female%2C%20with%20eggs%20inside.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20specimens%20were%20about%201%2C000%20years%20old%2C%20according%20to%20carbon%20testing%20carried%20out%20by%20researchers%20at%20the%20National%20Autonomous%20University%20of%20Mexico.%C2%A0Mr%20Maussan%20claimed%20they%20were%20not%20related%20to%20any%20species%20on%20Earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20under%20oath%20at%20the%20San%20Lazaro%20legislative%20palace%2C%20he%20said%2C%20''These%20specimens%20are%20not%20part%20of%20our%20terrestrial%20evolution%E2%80%A6%20These%20aren't%20beings%20that%20were%20found%20after%20a%20UFO%20wreckage.%20They%20were%20found%20in%20diatom%20%5Balgae%5D%20mines%2C%20and%20were%20later%20fossilised.''%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20there%20is%20a%20clear%20demonstration%20that%20we%20are%20dealing%20with%20non-human%20specimens%20that%20are%20not%20related%20to%20any%20other%20species%20in%20our%20world%20and%20that%20all%20possibilities%20are%20open%20for%20any%20scientific%20institution...%20to%20investigate%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20multiple%20UFO%20and%20forensics%20experts%20slammed%20the%20claims%20as%20''unsubstantiated''%20and%20a%20''hoax''.%20Some%20academics%20and%20archaeologists%20have%20suggested%20the%20%26quot%3Bbodies%26quot%3B%20are%20simply%20the%20ancient%20remains%20of%20mummified%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20physicist%20and%20presenter%20Professor%20Brian%20Cox%2C%20who%20was%20among%20the%20critics%2C%20has%20claimed%20that%20they%20were%20%C2%A0%26quot%3Bway%20too%20humanoid%26quot%3B%20to%20be%20genuine%2C%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fmummified-alien-corpses-are-from-single-skeletons-and-were-not-assembled-mexican-doctors-say-12964858%5C%22%3ESky%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%20He%20also%20has%20been%20calling%20for%20a%20sample%20to%20be%20sent%20to%20the%20biotechnology%20company%2023andme%20for%20independent%20verification.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20unlikely%20that%20an%20intelligent%20species%20that%20evolved%20on%20another%20planet%20would%20look%20like%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695148440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fes3inaqo_mexico-aliens-reuters_625x300_14_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Flab-tests-carried-out-on-mexicos-alien-bodies-no-evidence-of-any-assembly-4405402%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dr%20Jose%20de%20Jesus%20Zalce%20Benitez%20said%20that%20the%20laboratory%20tests%20have%20shown%20that%20''there%20is%20no%20evidence%20of%20any%20assemb