had%20alleged%20the%20involvement%20of%20%26quot%3Bagents%20of%20the%20Indian%20government%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Sikh%20separatist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20--%20said%20he%20was%20not%20looking%20to%20%26quot%3Bprovoke%26quot%3B%20India%20or%20%26quot%3Bescalate%26quot%3B%20tension%2C%20but%20wants%20New%20Delhi%20to%20take%20the%20killing%20of%20the%20separatist%20with%20%26quot%3Butmost%20seriousness%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20looking%20to%20provoke%20or%20escalate%2C%26quot%3B%20Justin%20Trudeau%20told%20reporters%20today.%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20work%20with%20the%20government%20of%20India%20to%20lay%20everything%20clear%20and%20to%20ensure%20there%20are%20proper%20processes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20rejected%20Mr%20Trudeau's%20claims.%20%26quot%3BAllegations%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India's%20involvement%20in%20any%20act%20of%20violence%20in%20Canada%20are%20absurd%20and%20motivated%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20foreign%20ministry%20has%20said.%C2%A0%20As%20the%20matter%20escalated%2C%20Canada%20and%20India%20each%20expelled%20a%20senior%20diplomat%20of%20the%20other%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%2045%2C%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20banned%20Khalistan%20Tiger%20Force%20and%20one%20of%20India's%20most-wanted%20terrorists%2C%20was%20shot%20dead%20by%20two%20unidentified%20gunmen%20on%20June%2018.%20He%20was%20killed%20outside%20a%20gurdwara%20in%20Surrey%20in%20the%20western%20Canadian%20province%20of%20British%20Columbia.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695146160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2018-02%2Fjustin-trudeau-pm-modi-in-canada-twitter_650x400_61519202560.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexercise-caution-canada-warns-citizens-about-travel-to-india-amid-row-4405244%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Canada%20today%20updated%20the%20travel%20advisory%20to%20India%20amid%20escalating%20ten