0that%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Trudeau%20told%20the%20Canadian%20parliament%20that%20security%20agencies%20were%20following%20credible%20allegations%20that%20Indian%20agents%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20murder%20of%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20a%20pro-Khalistani%20activist%20who%20was%20wanted%20in%20India%20and%20was%20shot%20dead%20outside%20a%20gurudwara%20in%20Surrey%2C%20British%20Columbia%20in%20June%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Canadian%20prime%20minister%20said%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20Ottawa%20will%20remain%20%E2%80%9Ccalm.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99re%20going%20to%20remain%20grounded%20in%20our%20democratic%20principles%20and%20values%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20going%20to%20follow%20the%20evidence%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20Canadians%20have%20a%20right%20to%20know%20and%20need%20to%20know%20when%20things%20are%20going%20on%20like%20this.%20And%20that%E2%80%99s%20why%20we%20made%20the%20decision%20to%20%5Breveal%5D%20this.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20CBC%2C%20Trudeau%2C%20talking%20about%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20announcement%2C%20said%20that%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20intelligence%20agencies%20%E2%80%9Chave%20been%20working%20on%20their%20analysis%20over%20the%20summer%20and%20he%20wanted%20to%20first%20alert%20allies%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20make%20sure%20we%20took%20the%20time%20to%20talk%20with%20our%20allies%20and%20share%20what%20we%20knew.%20We%20wanted%20to%20make%20sure%20we%20fully%20shared%20with%20the%20government%20of%20India%20the%20seriousness%20and%20depth%20of%20our%20occupation%20and%20indeed%20conclusions%E2%80%A6%20We%20are%20going%20to%20follow%20the%20evidence%20and%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20work%20is%20one%20to%20hold%20people%20to%20account%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theglobeandmail.com%2Fpolitics%2Farticle-conservative-leader-pierre-poilievre-urges-pm-trudeau-to-re