20In%20Armed%20Forces%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20woman%20officer%20can%20be%20posted%20in%20Siachen%2C%20a%20man%20can%20also%20be%20employed%20as%20a%20nurse%20in%20the%20Army%2C%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20observed%20on%20Tuesday%20as%20it%20pitched%20for%20gender%20equality%20in%20the%20armed%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20Satish%20Chandra%20Sharma%20and%20Justice%20Sanjeev%20Narula%20was%20hearing%20a%20petition%20about%20the%20alleged%20unconstitutional%20practice%20of%20having%20only%20women%20nurses%20in%20military%20establishments.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdditional%20Solicitor%20General%20Aishwarya%20Bhati%2C%20representing%20the%20Centre%2C%20said%20the%20practices%20in%20the%20Army%20are%20based%20on%20long-standing%20traditions.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%20She%2C%20however%2C%20said%20the%20government%20has%20just%20now%20brought%20in%20legislation%20to%20grant%2033%20per%20cent%20reservation%20to%20women%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20assemblies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20in%20parliament...%20On%20one%20hand%2C%20you%20are%20talking%20about%20empowering%20women%20and%20on%20the%20other%2C%20you%20are%20saying%20men%20cannot%20join%20as%20nurses...%20If%20a%20woman%20(officer)%20can%20be%20posted%20in%20Siachen%2C%20then%20a%20man%20can%20work%20in%20R%26amp%3BR%20(Hospital)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20also%20said%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20permitted%20women%20to%20join%20the%20National%20Defence%20Academy%20and%20it%20has%20time%20and%20again%20held%20that%20there%20should%20be%20no%20gender%20bias.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBhati%20told%20the%20bench%20the%20central%20government%20has%20filed%20its%20response%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Amit%20George%2C%20representing%20the%20petitioner%20Indian%20Professional%20Nurses%20Association%2C%20said%20now%20there%20are%20male%20nurses%20in%20all%20hospitals%20and%20even%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20said%20the%20practice%20of%20excluding%20one%20gender%20from%20the%20services%20has%20no%20place%20even%20in%20a%20military%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20High%20Court%20said%20it%20is%20an%20important%20issue%20which%20requires%20deliberation%20and%20listed%20the%20petition%20for%20further%20hearing%20in%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20High%20Court%20had%20earlier%20sought%20the%20Centre's%20stand%20on%20the%20plea%20challenging%20the%20%26quot%3Billegal%20practice%26quot%3B%20of%20appointing%20only%20women%20as%20military%20nurses.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20plea%2C%20the%20association%20has%20said%20there%20are%20several%20thousand%20trained%20and%20qualified%20male%20nurses%20in%20India%20and%20their%20omission%20from%20the%20nursing%20corps%20of%20the%20Army%20was%20%26quot%3Bunjustifiable%20and%20unconstitutional%20inasmuch%20as%20it%20deprives%20them%20of%20an%20avenue%20of%20employment%20and%20professional%20advancement%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20said%20omission%20also%20deprives%20the%20military%20and%20the%20nation%20of%20a%20large%20pool%20of%20committed%20professionals%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20petition%2C%20filed%20through%20advocates%20George%20and%20Rishabh%20Dheer%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20PIL%20has%20challenged%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Military%20Nursing%20Service%20Ordinance%2C%201943%20and%20the%20Military%20Nursing%20Service%20(India)%20Rules%2C%201944%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20they%20provide%20only%20for%20the%20appointment%20of%20women%20as%20nurses.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20contended%20the%20ordinance%20and%20the%20rules%20%26quot%3Balso%20perpetuate%20the%20stigmatisation%20and%20ostracism%20of%20male%20nurses%2C%20by%20singling%20them%20out%20and%20making%20them%20feel%20unwanted%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20said%20such%20discrimination%20is%20contrary%20to%20the%20constitutional%20scheme%20and%20is%2C%20therefore%2C%20%26quot%3Bex-facie%20unconstitutional%2C%20illegal%20and%20arbitrary%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20the%20high%20court%20termed%20as%20%26quot%3Bgender%20discrimination%26quot%3B%20the%20Indian%20Army's%20practice%20of%20having%20only%20women%20in%20its%20nursing%20service%20while%20granting%20time%20to%20the%20Centre%20to%20decide%20on%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695141540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-12%2Fjustice-generic-court-generic_650x400_61513069872.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-high-court-women-can-be-posted-in-siachen-men-can-also-work-as-nurses-in-army-gender-equality-armed-forces-4404563%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20a%20woman%20officer%20can%20be%20posted%20in%20Siachen%2C%20a%20man%20can%20also%20be%20employed%20as%20a%20nurse%20in%20the%20Army%2C%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20observed%20on%20Tuesday%20as%20it%20pitched%20for%20gender%20equality%20in%20the%20armed%20forces.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-high-court-women-can-be-posted-in-siachen-men-can-also-work-as-nurses-in-army-gender-equality-armed-forces-4404563%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-high-court-women-can-be-posted-in-siachen-men-can-also-work-as-nurses-in-army-gender-equality-armed-forces-4404563%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-high-court-women-can-be-posted-in-siachen-men-can-also-work-as-nurses-in-army-gender-equality-armed-forces-4404563%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Celebs%20arrive%20at%20Antilia%20for%20Ganpati%20celebration%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695141077000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22