ly%20decimated%20Sri%20Lanka%20to%20help%20India%20win%20the%20eighth%20Asia%20Cup%20title.%20After%20speedster%20Mohammed%20Siraj's%20fiery%20spell%20decimated%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20the%20opening%20duo%20of%20Shubman%20Gill%20and%20Ishan%20Kishan's%20flawless%20fifty-run%20partnership%20ensured%20India%20won%20Asia%20Cup%20by%20ten%20wickets.%20%26quot%3BDo%20you%20think%20I%20need%20to%20say%20anything%20more%20than%20what%20people%20are%20saying.%20What%20a%20fantastic%20cricket%20being%20played.%20I%20think%20as%20a%20cricketer%20I%20would%20like%20to%20see%20much%20closer%20games%20towards%20the%20World%20Cup%20but%20I%20think%20as%20a%20player%20dismiss%20them%20for%2030%20runs%20and%20win.%20But%20as%20a%20spectator%2C%20I%20would%20say%20it%20would%20be%20better%20if%20the%20game%20is%20close%2C%26quot%3B%20Kapil%20Dev%20said%20at%20a%20media%20event.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESiraj%20took%206%2F21%20in%20seven%20overs%20to%20bundle%20out%20Lankan%20Lions%20for%2050%20runs%20in%20just%2015.2%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKapil%20Dev%20said%20he%20has%20been%20wonderful.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20so%20happy%20that%20in%20the%20sub-continent%20all%2010%20wickets%20are%20being%20taken%20by%20our%20fast%20bowlers.%20I%20think%20that%20it%20is%20the%20cherry%20on%20the%20cake.%20There%20was%20a%20time%20when%20we%20used%20to%20depend%20on%20spinners%20but%20it%20is%20not%20anymore.%20That%20is%20why%20the%20team%20has%20become%20so%20good.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20skipper%20said%20it%20is%20more%20important%20right%20now%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20India%20first%20qualifies%20for%20the%20semi-final%20of%20the%20ICC%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20at%20home%20from%20October%205.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20if%20we%20come%20in%20the%20top%204%2C%20that%20is%20more%20important.%20You%20cannot%20say%2C%20right%20now%2C%20we%20are%20favourites.%20Our%20team%20is%20very%20good.%20We%20have%20to%20work%20very%20hard.%20I%20know%20about%20my%20team.%20I%20do%20not%20know%20about%20other%20teams...Indian%20team%20is%20ready%20to%20play%20and%20win%20the%20Championship.%20More%20than%20India%20winning%20the%20World%20Cup%20I%20want%20them%20to%20come%20out%20(to)%20dominate.%20I%20think%20that%20is%20what%20we%20look%20for%20in%20the%20future.%20I%20think%20the%20Indian%20team%20as%20far%20as%20I%20am%20concerned%2C%20are%20ready%20to%20play%20and%20win%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKapil%20Dev%20said%20that%20ahead%20of%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20injuries%20and%20keep%20players%20safe.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20needs%20to%20be%20careful%20of%20injuries.%20Any%20team%20is%20badly%20affected%20if%20two%20of%20its%20players%20get%20injured.%20This%20is%20the%20reason%20why%20a%20stroke%20of%20luck%20is%20required.%20If%20your%20main%20player%20is%20injured%20then%20the%20entire%20team%20falls%20apart%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnswering%20a%20query%20related%20to%20Hardik%20Pandya%2C%20a%20pace-bowling%20all-rounder%2C%C2%A0%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CLet%20us%20not%20talk%20about%20individuals.%20It%20is%20a%20team%20game%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20possible%20inclusion%20of%20players%20like%20Shikhar%20Dhawan%20and%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%2C%20Kapil%20Dev%20said%20that%20selectors%20have%20a%20better%20understanding%20of%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20need%20to%20talk%20about%20those%20who%20aren't%20there.%20Selectors%20are%20better%20than%20us%20because%20they%20put%20their%20heads%20together%20and%20pick%20the%20best%20team%E2%80%A6%20I%20think%20they%20collectively%20decided%20that%20this%20is%20the%20best%20team%20and%20we%20need%20to%20support%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKapil%20Dev%20lauded%20young%20opener%20Shubman%20Gill%20for%20his%20consistent%20performances%20as%20an%20opener%20this%20year.%20In%20the%20Asia%20Cup%2C%20he%20ended%20as%20the%20leading%20run-scorer%20with%20302%20runs%20in%20six%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%20above%2075%20with%20a%20century%20and%20two%20fifties.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShubman%20Gill%20is%20a%20youngster%20we%20all%20can%20look%20upto.%20Very%20very%20proud%20to%20have%20a%20player%20in%20Indian%20cricket%20of%20that%20ability%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%201%2C586%20runs%20in%2034%20international%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%2049.56%20with%20six%20tons%20and%20five%20fifties%20in%2037%20innings%2C%20Gill%20is%20India's%20best%20batter%20this%20year.%20He%20has%20done%20well%20particularly%20in%20ODIs%2C%20scoring%201%2C052%20runs%20in%2018%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%2070.13%2C%20with%20four%20tons%20and%20four%20fifties.%20This%20includes%20a%20double%20century%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695134700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fvt64uvvo_mohammed-siraj-has-claimed-six-wickets_625x300_17_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fcannot-say-we-are-favourites-kapil-devs-honest-take-on-india-ahead-of-cricket-world-cup-2023-4401915%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20legendary%20cricketer%20said%20that%20it%20is%20important%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20India%20first%20qualifies%20for%20the%20semi-final%20of%20the%20ICC%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20at%20home%20from%20October%205.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fcannot-say-we-are-favourites-kapil-devs-honest-take-on-india-ahead-of-cricket-world-cup-2023-4401915%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fcannot-say-we-are-favourites-kapil-devs-honest-take-on-india-ahead-of-cricket-world-cup-2023-4401915%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsport