3Cp%3EThe%20spat%20deals%20a%20fresh%20blow%20to%20diplomatic%20ties%2C%20with%20New%20Delhi%20unhappy%20over%20Sikh%20separatist%20activity%20in%20Canada.%20It%20now%20threatens%20trade%20ties%20too%2C%20with%20talks%20on%20a%20proposed%20trade%20deal%20frozen%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695133980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-02%2Fn0psbj18_canada-justin-trudeau-afp_625x300_22_February_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcanada-pm-justin-trudeau-amid-huge-row-not-trying-to-provoke-india-but-want-answers-4404622%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Canada%20is%20not%20trying%20to%20provoke%20India%20by%20suggesting%20its%20agents%20were%20linked%20to%20the%20murder%20of%20a%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20but%20Ottawa%20wants%20New%20Delhi%20to%20address%20the%20issue%20properly%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20said%20on%20Tuesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcanada-pm-justin-trudeau-amid-huge-row-not-trying-to-provoke-india-but-want-answers-4404622%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Fan%20Celebrating%20India's%20Goal%20vs%20China%20Told%20To%20Sit%20Down.%20Then...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20men's%20Indian%20football%20team%20began%20their%20Asian%20Games%20campaign%20on%20a%20forgettable%20note%20on%20Tuesday%20as%20they%20lost%20to%20hosts%20China%201-5.%20Giao%20Tianyi%20(17th%20min)%2C%20Dai%20Weijun%20(51st%20min)%2C%20Tao%20Qianglong%20(72nd%20and%2075th%20minute)%20and%20Hao%20Fang%20(90%2B2)%20scored%20for%20China.%20Rahul%20KP%20(45%2B1%20minute)%20scored%20the%20only%20goal%20for%20India%20in%20the%20first%20half%20from%20an%20acute%20angle.%20It%20was%20a%20great%20strike%20that%20ensured%20that%20India%20go%20into%20the%20half-time%20ties%201-1%20with%20China.%20However%2C%20the%20second-half%20was%20completely%20owned%20by%20China.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%20one%20goal%20by%20Rahul%20was%20enough%20to%20put%20the%20Indian%20fans%20present%20at%20Huanglong%20Sports%20Centre%20Stadium%20in%20Hangzhou%20on%20their%20feet.%20One%20such%20Indian%20fan%20got%20excited%20after%20the%20strike%20and%20started%20celebrating.%20One%20of%20the%20stadium%20attendants%20told%20him%20to%20sit%20down%20but%20he%20continues%20celebrating.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%7C%20WHAT%20A%20GOALLLLL%20RAHUL%20KP!%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frahulkp_r7_%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40rahulkp_r7_%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FtZLFnGNADW%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FtZLFnGNADW%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Rohit%20Sharma%20(%40arvindkaliravna)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Farvindkaliravna%2Fstatus%2F1704110819251003447%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2019%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20heartening%20to%20see%20a%20third-string%20team%20holding%20the%20title%20contenders%20on%20an%20even%20keel%20during%20the%20first%2045%20minutes%2C%20which%20saw%20Indian%20custodian%20Gurmeet%20Singh%20Chahal%20valiantly%20save%20a%20spot-kick%20taken%20by%20rival%20captain%20Zhu%20Chenjie.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20now%20need%20to%20beat%20Bangladesh%20and%20Myanmar%20in%20their%20remaining%20two%20games%20to%20qualify%20for%20the%20second%20round.%20Myanmar%20beat%20Bangladesh%204-2%20in%20another%20game%20in%20this%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHaving%20reached%20the%20Games%20Village%20late%20on%20Monday%20evening%2C%20the%20third-string%20Indian%20team%2C%20with%20not%20even%20four%20specialist%20defenders%20in%20their%20ranks%2C%20didn't%20have%20enough%20co-ordination%20amongst%20themselves.%20They%20looked%20jet-lagged%2C%20not%20rested%20enough%20and%20there%20was%20no%20way%20that%20there%20could%20have%20been%20a%20miracle.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20gulf%20in%20class%20and%20quality%20was%20evident%20and%20most%20of%20the%20Chinese%20attacks%20happened%20from%20India's%20wide%20left%20(China's%20right%20flank)%20side%2C%20which%20was%20being%20manned%20by%20Sumit%20Rathi.%20It%20became%20a%20free-ride%20for%20the%20Chinese%20attackers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20the%20humidity%20and%20lack%20of%20training%20time%20had%20its%20effect%20as%20the%20Indians%20didn't%20have%20the%20legs%20to%20last%20beyond%20the%20first%20hour.%20And%2C%20once%20the%20second%20goal%20was%20scored%20due%20to%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sandesh%20Jhingan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Fplayers%2F106573-sandesh-jhingan-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESandesh%20Jhingan%3C%2Fa%3E's%20poor%20anticipation%2C%20the%20floodgates%20opened.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJhingan%20was%20also%20responsible%20for%20another%20goal%20when%20he%20had%20a%20brain%20fade%20and%20wanted%20to%20dribble%20his%20team%20past%20the%20danger%20in%20his%20own%20penalty%20box%20and%20committed%20harakiri.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20players%20suffered%20from%20cramps%20due%20to%20humidity%20and%2C%20obviously%2C%20not%20having%20enough%20time%20to%20warm-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESkipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sunil%20Chhetri%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Fplayers%2F106840-sunil-chhetri-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESunil%20Chhetri%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20on%20the%20pitch%20for%2085%20minutes%20and%2C%20save%20a%20pile%20driver%20that%20sailed%20way%20over%20the%20horizontal%2C%20he%20had%20precious%20little%20to%20do%20with%20a%20literally%20non-existent%20feeder%20line%2C%20which%20concentrated%20on%20creating%20a%20chaos%20in%20the%20defensive%20third%20to%20thwart%20the%20wave%20of%20Chinese%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20silver-lining%20was%20the%20goal%20by%20Rahul%20KP%2C%20the%20former%20U-17%20World%20Cupper%2C%20who%20was%20freed%20on%20the%20wide%20right%20by%20Abdul%20Rabeeh%20and%20the%20Kerala%20Blasters%20player%20sprinted%20and%20smashed%20it%20in%20from%20near%20zero%20degree%2C%20much%20to%20the%20awe%20of%20a%20capacity%20home%20crowd.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndians%20went%20into%20the%20break%201-1%20but%20the%20wheels%20came%20off%20in%20the%20second%20half%2C%20and%20it%20was%20more%20due%20to%20fatigue.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20these%20players%20are%20not%20even%20first-choice%20substitutes%20for%20their%20respective%20ISL%20clubs%20and%20it%20was%20evident%20that%20match%20fitness%20was%20a%20big%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20then%20their%20lack%20of%20quality%20can't%20be%20blamed%20on%20them%20but%20on%20the%20custodians%20of%20Indian%20football%20including%20Football%20Sports%20Development%20Limited%20(FSDL)%20putting%20a%20spanner%20in%20AIFF's%20efforts%20of%20conjuring%20the%20best%20bunch%20for%20the%20continental%20showpiece%2C%20showing%20the%20FIFA%20rule%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695133920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F8ar9c298_indian-flag-asian-games_625x300_19_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasian-games-2023%2Fasian-games-fan-celebrating-indias-goal-vs-hosts-china-at-asian-games-told-to-sit-down-then-this-happens-eatch-4404627%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20men's%20Indian%20football%20team%20began%20their%20Asian%20Games%20campaign%20on%20a%20forgettable%20note%20on%20Tuesday%20as%20they%20lost%20to%20hosts%20China%201-5%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasian-games-2023%2Fasian-games-fan-celebrating-indias-goal-vs-hosts-china-at-asian-games-told-to-sit-down-then-this-happens-eatch-4404627%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasian-games-2023%2Fasian-games-fan-celebrating-indias-goal-vs-h