werful%20jujutsu%20wizard%20in%20'Jujutsu%20Kaisen'%2C%20has%20vulnerabilities%20that%20can%20be%20exploited.%20Hana%20Kurusu's%20Technique%20Nullification%20can%20nullify%20Gojo's%20defenses.%20The%20Inverted%20Spear%20of%20Heaven%20can%20pierce%20his%20shield%20created%20by%20the%20Limitless%20Technique.%20Gojo%20can%20also%20become%20fatigued%2C%20leaving%20him%20susceptible%20to%20physical%20harm.%20The%20Prison%20Realm%20can%20immobilize%20and%20seal%20him.%20Additionally%2C%20emotional%20distress%20can%20cause%20Gojo%20to%20lose%20focus%20and%20become%20vulnerable.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fetimes-anime-update-gojo-satorus-5-weaknesses-in-jujutsu-kaisen%2Farticleshow%2F103787786.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%227%20Leopard%20Cubs%20Die%20At%20Bengaluru%20Biological%20Park%20After%20Virus%20Attack%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESeven%20leopard%20cubs%20have%20died%20at%20Bannerghatta%20Biological%20Park%20in%20Bengaluru%20after%20being%20infected%20by%20a%20highly%20contagious%20virus%2C%20officials%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFeline%20panleukopenia%20(FP)%20is%20a%20viral%20disease%20of%20cats%20caused%20by%20the%20feline%20parvovirus.%20Kittens%20are%20most%20severely%20affected%20by%20the%20virus%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20officials%2C%20the%20first%20outbreak%20was%20reported%20on%20August%2022.%20The%20seven%20cubs%20were%20aged%20between%20three%20and%20eight%20months.%20All%20of%20them%20were%20vaccinated%20but%20succumbed%20during%20the%20course%20of%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EExecutive%20Director%20of%20Bannerghatta%20Biological%20Park%2C%20AV%20Surya%20Sen%20said%20though%20the%20seven%20cubs%20were%20vaccinated%2C%20they%20were%20still%20infected.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20now%20under%20control%20and%20in%20the%20last%2015%20days%2C%20no%20deaths%20have%20been%20reported.%20We%20have%20completely%20broken%20the%20chain%20and%20taken%20all%20necessary%20measures.%20We%20followed%20all%20the%20required%20procedure%20and%20also%20held%20discussions%20with%20all%20our%20senior%20veterinarians.%20All%20correct%20course%20of%20action%20was%20taken.%20Also%2C%20we%20have%20ensured%20hygiene%20of%20the%20entire%20zoo%20and%20the%20rescue%20centre%20was%20completely%20sanitised%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20infection%20was%20reported%20on%20August%2022%20and%20within%20a%20span%20of%2015%20days%2C%20these%20seven%20virus%20infected%20cubs%20died.%20We%20had%20released%20nine%20leopard%20cubs%20into%20the%20Safari%20area%2C%20out%20of%20which%20four%20got%20infected%20and%20died.%20Three%20other%20cubs%20at%20the%20rescue%20centre%20also%20got%20infected%20and%20died%20during%20the%20course%20of%20treatment.%20All%20those%20infected%20died%20within%20a%20span%20of%20two%20weeks%20despite%20being%20given%20proper%20treatment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20nature%20of%20virus%2C%20the%20official%20said%20once%20infected%20by%20Feline%20panleukopenia%20virus%2C%20the%20intestine%20of%20the%20animal%20gets%20completely%20affected.%20They%20develop%20severe%20diarrhea%2C%20vomiting%20and%20dehydration%20which%20ultimately%20leads%20to%20death.%20It%20spreads%20faster%20and%20the%20infected%20animal%20dies%20within%20four%20to%20five%20days.%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695132780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-03%2F4l42ebq_leopard-cub-generic_625x300_13_March_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkarnataka-news%2F7-leopard-cubs-die-at-bengaluru-biological-