aced%20with%20this%20reality%2C%20I%20made%20a%20conscious%20decision%20to%20stop%20appearing%20on%20specific%20television%20channels%2C%20starting%20with%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20Now%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20never%20saw%20%3Cem%3ERepublic%20TV%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20a%20platform%20for%20truth%20or%20journalism%2C%20so%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20feel%20compelled%20to%20make%20a%20similar%20announcement%20regarding%20them.%20But%20for%20those%20who%20still%20do%2C%20I%20would%20like%20to%20furnish%20two%20studies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20as%20per%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhpuniv.ac.in%2Fhpuniv%2Fupload%2Fuploadfiles%2Ffiles%2FHPUJ-June-2022-issue.pdf%23page%3D110%5C%22%3Equantitative%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Ashish%20Sharma%20and%20Sandeep%20Kumar%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EAlthough%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3ERepublic%20TV%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98s%20debates%20haven%E2%80%99t%20covered%20any%20pressing%20issues%20that%20affect%20society%2C%20such%20as%20the%20economy%2C%20education%2C%20employment%2C%20or%20health%20conditions.%20Instead%2C%20they%20primarily%20focus%20on%20the%20core%20issue%20of%20politics%20which%20mostly%20attacks%20the%20opposition%20and%20any%20group%20or%20individuals%20opposing%20the%20ideology%20of%20the%20ruling%20government.%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20Ashwini%20Ramesh%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fprofile%2FRijitha-R%2Fpublication%2F358730635_THE_IMPACT_OF_SOCIAL_MEDIA_MARKETING_ON_CONSUMER_PURCHASE_INTENTION%2Flinks%2F63f725205749505945377a51%2FTHE-IMPACT-OF-SOCIAL-MEDIA-MARKETING-ON-CONSUMER-PURCHASE-INTENTION.pdf%23page%3D26%5C%22%3Ecrunched%20the%20numbers%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20her%20comparative%20assessment%20holds%20that%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRepublic%20TV%3Cem%3E%20involves%20in%20media%20framing%20the%20most%20as%20compared%20to%20%3C%2Fem%3EIndia%20Today%3Cem%3E%20or%20%3C%2Fem%3ENDTV%2024%C3%977%3Cem%3E%20news%20channels.%20Conflict%20and%20anti-journalistic%20objectivity%20frames%20are%20the%20most%20popular%20frames%20for%20prime-time%20television%20debates%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20as%20if%20these%20choices%20have%20been%20easy%20or%20certain.%20Even%20before%202021%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20in%20a%20similar%20situation%20concerning%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20Now%3C%2Fem%3E.%20It%20was%20during%20Faye%20D%E2%80%99Souza%E2%80%99s%20tenure%20at%20%3Cem%3EMirror%20Now%3C%2Fem%3E%20when%20I%20decided%20to%20halt%20my%20appearances%20there%20due%20to%20no%20fault%20of%20theirs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FbBNk4YLkECM%3Fsi%3DABsnw-IpqKzxdvYC%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20a%20period%20when%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20Now%3C%2Fem%3E%20targeted%20civil%20society%20activists%20and%20human%20rights%20defenders%2C%20labelling%20them%20as%20%E2%80%9Canti-national%E2%80%9D%20for%20their%20dissenting%20views.%20Selective%20facts%20from%20their%20public%20and%20personal%20lives%20were%20unveiled%2C%20accompanied%20by%20doctored%20videos%20and%20unfair%20characterisations%2C%20creating%20public%20turmoil%20and%20eroding%20trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETragically%2C%20these%20broadcasts%20resulted%20in%20real-world%20harm%2C%20including%20criminal%20prosecutions%2C%20loss%20of%20livelihoods%20and%20the%20destruction%20of%20homes%20for%20many%20individuals.%20I%20grappled%20with%20internal%20moral%20considerations%2C%20as%20the%20progressive%20broadcast%20by%20%3Cem%3EMirror%20Now%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20under%20the%20umbrella%20of%20the%20Times%20Group%2C%20which%20also%20operated%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20Now%3C%2Fem%3E.%20While%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20recall%20the%20exact%20decision-making%20process%2C%20I%20opted%20to%20increase%20my%20contributions%20to%20national%20newspapers%20by%20shifting%20time%20from%20TV%20debates.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20concerns%20about%20certain%20newspapers%20advancing%20a%20majoritarian%20agenda%2C%20there%20was%20a%20marked%20difference%20between%20them%20and%20late-night%20primetime%20shows.%20Concerns%2C%20if%20any%2C%20were%20more%20subtle%20and%20mostly%20on%20themes%20of%20neoliberalism%20and%20market-based%20interventions.%20Here%2C%20I%20continue%20to%20benefit%20from%20these%20platforms%20for%20professional%20growth%20through%20increased%20visibility%20and%20the%20opportunity%20to%20publish%20commentary%20on%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20public%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20this%2C%20I%20do%20not%20have%20to%20be%20in%20complete%20political%20and%20moral%20agreement%2C%20but%20refuse%20to%20be%20an%20accessory%20to%20a%20media%20entity%20directing%20threats%20and%20hate%20speech.%20Through%20these%20instances%2C%20I%20maintained%20a%20clear%20boundary%20%E2%80%93%20I%20steadfastly%20refused%20to%20participate%20in%20debates%20hosted%20by%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20Now%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fapar1984%2Fstatus%2F1702992257996255301%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Ereiterated%20my%20stance%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20an%20addition.%20I%20believe%20that%20not%20only%20should%20more%20experts%20and%20panellists%20be%20deliberate%20in%20their%20choice%20of%20anchors%20and%20television%20platforms%2C%20but%20also%20make%20it%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fgandhis-1926-call-for-boycott-of-newspapers-spreading-hatred-resonates-with-indias-decision%5C%22%3EGandhi%E2%80%99s%201926%20Call%20for%20Boycott%20of%20Newspapers%20Spreading%20Hatred%20Resonates%20With%20INDIA%E2%80%99s%20Decision%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETransparency%20serves%20their%20own%20ethical%20obligations%20but%20also%20fosters%20greater%20accountability%20towards%20themselves%20and%20broadcasters.%20This%20is%20not%20mere%20%E2%80%9Cvirtue%20signalling%E2%80%9D%3B%20for%20many%2C%20it%20will%20entail%20a%20cost%2C%20as%20it%20means%20forgoing%20airtime%20and%20opportunities%20that%20could%20lead%20to%20personal%20advancement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20such%20public%20declarations%20may%20not%20be%20flawless%2C%20they%20aim%20to%20reduce%20inconsistencies%20and%20build%20solidarity.%20Inevitably%2C%20private%20individuals%20may%20make%20exceptions%20to%20their%20non-participation%20stance%20to%20support%20junior%20journalists%20or%20address%20issues%20of%20strategic%20or%20emotional%20importance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20public%20statements%20can%20serve%20as%20a%20check%20against%20undue%20compromise.%20I%20acknowledge%20that%20I%20am%20not%20the%20first%20to%20make%20this%20call%2C%20but%20I%20believe%20that%20more%20voices%20taking%20this%20step%20and%20repeatedly%20stating%20it%20in%20public%20is%20a%20meaningful%20contribution%20towards%20the%20restoration%20of%20constitutional%20sanity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20media%20landscape%20under%20constant%20attack%20by%20primetime%20anchors%2C%20such%20actions%20even%20when%20minor%20gain%20importance.%20Broken%20news%20will%20only%20be%20fixed%20by%20collective%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fa-gupta%5C%22%3EApar%20Gupta%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20advocate%20and%20the%20Founder%20Director%20of%20the%20Internet%20Freedom%20Foundation%2C%20Delhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695130516000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19135234%2FNews-studio.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fmore-panellists-must-be-deliberate-in-their-choice-of-anchors-and-tv-platforms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22More%20voices%20taking%20this%20step%20and%20repeatedly%20stating%20it%20in%20public%20is%20a%20meaningful%20contribution%20towards%20the%20restoration%20of%20constitutional%20sanity.%20In%20a%20media%20landscape%20under%20constant%20attack%20by%20primetime%20anchors%2C%20such%20actions%20even%20when%20minor%20gain%20importance.%20Broken%20news%20will%20only%20be%20fixed%20by%20collective%20action.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fmore-panellists-must-be-deliberate-in-their-choice-of-anchors-and-tv-platforms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amit%20Shah's%20%26quot%3BFriendly%20Parties%26quot%3B%20Jab%20As%20Congress%20Claims%20%26quot%3BOur%26quot%3B%20Women's%20Bill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnion%20Home%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Famit-shah%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmit%20Shah%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0ripped%20into%20the%20Congress%20(he%20did%20not%20name%20the%20party)%20after%20it%20attacked%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20for%20%26quot%3Bdelays%26quot%3B%20in%20tabling%20the%20landmark%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fwomen%2527s-reservation-bill%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewomen's%20reservation%20bill%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20was%20presented%20by%20the%20Union%20Law%20Minister%20in%20Parliament%20today.%20The%20Congress%20had%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20dragging%20its%20feet%20over%20the%20bill%20in%20search%20of%20an%20image%20boost%20ahead%20of%20next%20year's%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20hailed%20the%20%26quot%3Bunwavering%20commitment%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%26quot%3B%20and%20mocked%20the%20Congress%20for%20%26quot%3Bfriendly%20parties%20(that%20prevented)%26quot%3B%20the%20bill%20from%20being%20tabled.%20The%20bill%20was%20cleared%20by%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20in%202010%20(when%20Manmohan%20Singh%20was%20PM)%20but%20it%20failed%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20hurdle%20after%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20and%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20opposed%20it.%20Both%20were%20(and%20are%20now)%20allies%20of%20t