s-4402789%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIt%20(the%20bill)%20is%20ours...%20%3Cem%3Eapna%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20Since%20then%20several%20Congress%20leaders%20have%20taken%20pains%20to%20point%20out%20the%20bill%20was%20tabled%20in%20Parliament%20by%20the%20party-led%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20government%2013%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKapil%20Sibal%2C%20who%20quit%20the%20party%20in%20May%20last%20year%20in%20acrimonious%20circumstances%2C%20made%20the%20same%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20(the%20BJP)%20want%20a%20political%20advantage%20(for%20the%202024%20election)%20and%20want%20to%20tell%20women%20they%20did%20a%20'historic'%20thing.%20They%20should%20have%20done%20this%20in%202014%20(when%20PM%20Modi%20first%20came%20to%20power)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwomens-reservation-bill-pm-modi-new-parliament-jumla-betrayal-mahila-bewakoof-bana-opposition-on-womens-bill-%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BJumla%2C%20Betrayal%2C%20'%3Cem%3EMahila%20Bewakoof%20Bana%3C%2Fem%3E'%26quot%3B%3A%20Opposition%20On%20Women's%20Bill%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20so%20historic%20about%20this%3F%20There%20will%20be%20a%20census%20and%20delimitation%20before%20the%20bill%20is%20implemented.%20What%20if%20census%20and%20delimitation%20don't%20happen%3F%20They%20are%20just%20showing%20dreams%20to%20women%20-%20that%20they%20will%20get%20'reservation'%20in%202029.%20They%20(the%20BJP)%20can't%20think%20anything%20other%20than%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sibal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20On%20Women's%20Reservation%