%20for%20all.%20Visva-Bharati%20acknowledges%20India%E2%80%99s%20obligation%20to%20offer%20to%20others%20the%20hospitality%20of%20her%20best%20culture%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20accept%20from%20others%20their%20best%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rabindranath%20had%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETagore%E2%80%99s%20vision%20was%20for%20it%20to%20become%20a%20%E2%80%9Cseat%20of%20learning%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20this%20was%20embraced%20and%20continued%20by%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20and%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru.%20In%20a%20letter%20presented%20to%20Gandhi%20during%20his%20final%20visit%20to%20Shantiniketan%20in%20February%201940%2C%20Tagore%20fervently%20appealed%20for%20his%20protection%20and%20assurance%20of%20the%20institution%E2%80%99s%20permanence%2C%20stressing%20that%20it%20was%20a%20national%20treasure%20carrying%20the%20essence%20of%20his%20life%E2%80%99s%20work.%20In%20response%2C%20Gandhi%20assured%20that%20Visva-Bharati%20was%20indeed%20a%20national%20and%20international%20institution%20and%20pledged%20to%20work%20towards%20ensuring%20its%20enduring%20legacy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%201951%2C%20the%20Visva-Bharati%20Bill%20was%20passed%20in%20the%20parliament%2C%20making%20it%20a%20unitary%2C%20teaching%2C%20and%20residential%20university.%20During%20the%20parliamentary%20debate%2C%20both%20Prime%20Minister%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20and%20education%20minister%20Maulana%20Abul%20Kalam%20Azad%20emphasised%20the%20importance%20of%20preserving%20the%20institution%E2%80%99s%20unique%20environment%20and%20ideals%20of%20natural%20harmony%2C%20cultural%20richness%2C%20and%20global%20inclusivity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20288px)%2085vw%2C%20288px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19180105%2Fimage-5.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22288%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19180105%2Fimage-5.png%20539w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19180105%2Fimage-5-135x300.png%20135w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19180105%2Fimage-5-460x1024.png%20460w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-673786%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22641%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPosters%20on%20the%20Visva-Bharati%20University%20campus%2C%20alleging%20the%20V-C%20Bidyut%20Chakraborty%20of%20negligence%20and%20insult%20of%20the%20UNESCO%20team%20that%20had%20gone%20for%20assessment.%20Photo%3A%20Joydeep%20Sarkar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20no%20university%20in%20the%20world%20that%20has%20been%20declared%20a%20heritage%20site%20while%20education%20is%20ongoing.%20From%20that%20perspective%2C%20this%20is%20truly%20unique.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20all%20come%20together%20to%20work%20for%20Visva-Bharati%2C%20moving%20beyond%20the%20controversies%20around%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Bidyut%20Chakraborty%2C%20the%20Vice-Chancellor%20of%20the%20university.%20Chakraborty%E2%80%99s%20tenure%20has%20been%20marked%20with%20controversies%2C%20including%20a%20land%20dispute%20with%20Nobel%20laureate%20Amartya%20Sen%2C%20allegations%20of%20corruption%2C%20and%20his%20frequent%20lashings%20out%20at%20both%20teachers%20and%20students.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAttaining%20such%20a%20grand%20heritage%20status%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20pride%2C%20but%20safeguarding%20it%20carries%20an%20even%20greater%20responsibility%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Supriya%20Thakur%2C%20former%20principal%20of%20Patha%20Bhavan%20and%20a%20descendant%20of%20Rabindranath%20Tagore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERestoration%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKala%20Bhavan%2C%20the%20fine%20arts%20faculty%20of%20Visva-Bharati%20University%2C%20ranks%20among%20India%E2%80%99s%20top%20fine%20arts%20institutions%20and%20showcases%20a%20remarkable%20gallery%20with%2017%2C000%20original%20artworks%20by%20esteemed%20Indian%20and%20East%20Asian%20masters.%20However%2C%20the%20beautiful%20frescoes%2C%20sculptures%2C%20and%20murals%20by%20artists%20like%20Ramkinkar%20Baij%2C%20Nandalal%20Bose%2C%20and%20Benode%20Behari%20Mukherjee%20that%20adorn%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20complex%20are%20facing%20deterioration%20due%20to%20neglect.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20initial%20maintenance%20and%20preservation%20efforts%20have%20commenced%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20iconic%20Uttarayan%20complex%20housing%20Rabindranath%E2%80%99s%20residence%2C%20known%20as%20Shyamali%2C%20along%20with%20other%20structures%2C%20experts%20stress%20the%20importance%20of%20regular%20care%20and%20conservation%20to%20protect%20this%20artistic%20heritage.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20restoration%20initiative%20was%20initiated%20several%20decades%20ago%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20former%20Vice-Chancellor%20Sujit%20Basu%2C%20its%20progress%20has%20been%20relatively%20slow.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20happy%20for%20the%20heritage%20status.%20It%E2%80%99s%20another%20feather%20in%20Shantiniketan%E2%80%99s%20illustrious%20cap.%20While%20I%20had%20initiated%20the%20process%2C%20now%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20shared%20responsibility%20for%20everyone%20to%20uphold%20this%20recognition%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Basu.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFormer%20Kala%20Bhavan%20principal%20Prabir%20Biswas%2C%20who%20was%20once%20a%20part%20of%20the%20core%20committee%20for%20preservation%2C%20feels%20that%20significant%20changes%20should%20not%20be%20in%20the%20offing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20heritage%20tag%20would%20require%20such%20changes%2C%20such%20as%20not%20allowing%20sculptures%20to%20be%20touched%20and%20not%20blocking%20the%20pathways%20at%20Shantiniketan.%20The%20World%20Heritage%20Committee%20allocates%20funds%20for%20the%20conservation%20and%20supervision%20of%20the%20designated%20heritage%20area.%20If%20this%20money%20is%20used%20wisely%2C%20it%20will%20undoubtedly%20help%20in%20the%20preservation%20of%20many%20endangered%20artistic%20treasures%2C%E2%80%9D%20Biswas%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20the%20Bengali%20original%20by%20Aparna%20Bhattacharya.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695126880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19180152%2Fimage-2-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fvisva-bharati-university-unesco-living-heritage-art-craft%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20world's%20first%20living%20heritage%20university%20should%20use%20money%20wisely%20to%20preserve%20its%20wealth%20of%20art%20and%20crafts%2C%20say%20experts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fvisva-bharati-university-unesco-living-heritage-art-craft%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Libya%20flood%3A%20Video%20appears%20to%20show%20Libya%20mayor's%20house%20set%20on%20fire%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695126714000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F17F68%2Fproduction%2F_131125189_p0gffyrl.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-66856412%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20mayor's%20home%20was%20burnt%20to%20the%20ground%20as%20protesters%20demanded%20answers%20for%20last%20week's%20catastrophic%20flood.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A34%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-africa-66856412%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Starmer%20and%20Macron%20exchange%20gifts%20as%20they%20meet%20for%20first%20time%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695126660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22ht