0message%20will%20prevail.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELet%20me%20refer%20to%20that%20press%20release%20which%20you%20referred%20to%20earlier%2C%20which%20I%20said%20I%20would%20bring%20up%20later%2C%20issued%20by%20the%20News%20Broadcasters%20and%20Digital%20Association.%20They%20say%20that%20boycotting%20individual%20journalists%20amounts%20to%20%E2%80%9Cstifling%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression%20of%20the%20media%E2%80%9D.%20Now%20do%20you%20agree%2C%20or%20do%20you%20think%20this%20is%20a%20bit%20exaggerated%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20completely%20over%20the%20top%2C%20and%20it%20looks%20like%20they%E2%80%99re%20going%20out%20of%20their%20way%20to%20have%20that%20knife%20and%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20because%20they%20say%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20dangerous%20precedent.%20I%20have%20a%20chair%20with%20the%20text.%20They%20refer%20to%20these%20people%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%2014%20I%20guess%2C%20as%20some%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20top%20TV%20news%20personalities%2C%20seemingly%20in%20a%20laudatory%20way.%20The%20really%20over-the-top%20statement%20is%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20boycott%20of%20certain%20journalists%2Fanchors%20takes%20the%20nation%20back%20to%20the%20Emergency%20when%20the%20press%20was%20gagged%E2%80%9D.%20I%20mean%2C%20this%20is%20ridiculous%2C%20this%20statement%3B%20because%20I%20lived%20through%20the%20Emergency%2C%20there%20was%20total%20censorship.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F01145236%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-01-at-1.39.01-PM-e1693560384596.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F01145236%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-01-at-1.39.01-PM-e1693560384596.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fc