only%20deny%20but%20refuse%20to%20accept%20because%20these%20people%20continue%20as%20anchors%2C%20and%20these%20people%20are%20not%20just%20employed%20but%20well%20paid%3B%20and%20clearly%2C%20these%20anchors%20are%20fulfilling%20channel%20policy.%20Some%20channels%20deliberately%20have%20two%20sets%20of%20anchors%2C%20such%20as%20%3Cem%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20one%20section%20is%20of%20the%20Rahul%20Kanwals%20and%20Rajdeep%20Sardesais%2C%20who%20are%20secular%2C%20balanced%20and%20not%20sectarian%3B%20and%20then%20allegedly%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20using%20the%20word%20allegedly%20deliberately%2C%20the%20Shiv%20Aroors%20and%20the%20Gaurav%20Sawants%2C%20who%20can%20appeal%20to%20the%20Hindutva%20brigade.%20That%E2%80%99s%20general%20policy%20%E2%80%93%20we%20have%20therefore%20a%20spectrum%20that%20attracts%20people%20from%20whatever.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20thing%2C%20it%20makes%20sense%20from%20a%20commercial%20standpoint.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20if%20it%20really%20works%2C%20I%20have%20no%20idea.%20But%20suddenly%20those%20are%20the%20calculations%2C%20it%20appears%2C%20having%20this%20not%20to%20foster%20pluralism%2C%20not%20to%20encourage%20diversity%2C%20but%20to%20take%20care%20of%20commercial%20viability%20at%20a%20time%20when%20even%20television%20is%20facing%20huge%20challenges%2C%20revenue%20challenges%20and%20so%20on%2C%20especially%20news%20television%20in%20particular.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fas-india-bloc-defends-tv-anchor-boycott-list-as-non-cooperation-bjp-calls-it-emergency-mindset%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520list%2520named%2520Aditi%2520Tyagi%2CIndia%2520TV)%252C%2520Rubika%2520Liaquat%2520(%5C%22%3EAs%20INDIA%20Bloc%20Defends%20TV%20Anchor%20Boycott%20List%20as%20%E2%80%98Non-Cooperation%E2%80%99%2C%20BJP%20Calls%20it%20%E2%80%98Emergency%E2%80%99%20Mindset%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWould%20it%20not%20have%20been%20wiser%20to%20adopt%20a%20strategy%20that%20would%20be%20more%20likely%20to%2C%20not%20guaranteed%20but%20more%20likely%20to%2C%20silence%20hate-mongering%20on%20TV%20completely%3F%20If%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20had%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CChannels%20like%20A%2C%20B%2C%20C%2C%20D%20we%20will%20boycott%20completely%E2%80%9D%2C%C2%A0%20rather%20than%20choose%20the%20anchors%20you%E2%80%99ll%20boycott%2C%20then%20those%20channels%20would%20have%20had%20a%20very%20difficult%20time%20doing%20political%20programming%2C%20even%20worse%20when%20elections%20come.%20Therefore%2C%20you%20might%20have%20forced%20them%20to%20rethink%2C%20but%20if%20you%20pick%20the%20anchors%20then%20those%20anchors%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20communal%2C%20and%20you%20will%20be%20still%20going%20to%20other%20anchors%2C%20so%20the%20channel%20will%20still%20have%20you.%20In%20other%20words%2C%C2%A0%20the%20channel%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20really%20lost%2C%20but%20INDIA%20Alliance%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20gained%20very%20much.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20I%20get%20your%20point%2C%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20almost%20persuaded%20that%20distinction%20is%20very%20important%20%E2%80%93%20between%20sanctions%20against%20the%20channel%20and%20against%20individuals%2C%20because%20your%20point%20being%20that%20the%20channels%20want%20that.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20channels%20that%20created%20these%20anchors%2C%20in%20effect.%20They%20picked%20them%20and%20they%20also%20have%20both%20sides%20and%20on%20the%20spectrum%2C%20as%20you%20said.%20It%20depends%20on%20that%20strategy%2C%20I%20agree%20with%20you%20on%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFinally%2C%20I%20want%20to%20raise%20briefly%20before%20I%20end%20a%20deeper%20issue%2C%20but%20it%20is%20still%20connected%20to%20the%20INDIA%20Alliance%20boycott%20and%20controversy.%20You%20are%20a%20proprietor%20of%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20papers%20in%20the%20country%2C%20your%20family%20has%20been%20involved%20in%20running%20a%20paper%20and%20thinking%20about%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20institution%20for%20decades.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%201905%20to%20be%20precise.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%20you%20are%2C%20in%20fact%20over%20a%20century.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20I%20put%20this%20question%20to%20you%20%E2%80%93%20why%20do%20proprietors%20on%20television%20channels%20permit%20and%20even%20encourage%20hate-filled%20discussions%3F%20Is%20it%20because%20they%20themselves%20are%20full%20of%20hate%2C%20particularly%20for%20Muslims%3F%20Or%20is%20it%20secondly%20because%20they%20believe%20these%20discussions%20bring%20TRPs%2C%20advertising%20and%20therefore%20profit%2C%20so%20this%20is%20a%20commercial%20way%20of%20making%20money%3F%20Or%20is%20it%20possibly%20because%20these%20proprietors%20face%20enforcement%20directed%20and%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20cases%2C%20and%20this%20is%20a%20way%20of%20protecting%20themselves%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20I%20think%20the%20last%20is%20the%20most%20important%20factor%20in%20this.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20them%20believe%20in%20hate%20against%20Muslims%20and%20so%20on%2C%20at%20least%20people%20I%20know.%20But%20most%20of%20them%20have%20fallen%20in%20line%20because%20they%20are%20afraid.%20They%20also%20want%20favours%20from%20the%20government%3B%20advertising%20and%20other%20favors%20for%20businesses%2C%20so%20they%20want%20to%20be%20on%20the%20right%20side%20as%20they%20see%20it%20as%20the%20safe%20side.%20But%20the%20real%20fear%20is%20%E2%80%93%20I%20mean%2C%20there%20was%20a%20case%20of%20a%20major%20Hindi%20language%20newspaper%20which%20did%20exceptional%20work%20in%20covering%20bits%2C%20COVID-19%20deaths%20and%20then%20there%20was%20a%20raid%2C%20at%20least%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20I%20read%20in%20the%20press%2C%20and%20then%20they%20fell%20in%20line%20if%20it%E2%80%99s%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20that%20they%20want%20to%20suppress%20the%20truth%20%E2%80%93%20many%20of%20them%20are%20professionals%2C%20they%20have%20a%20tradition%20of%20good%20journalism%2C%20but%20something%20has%20happened%20just%20as%20during%20the%20Emergency.%20They%20caved%20in%20completely%2C%20almost%20without%20exception.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20buy%20the%20story%20that%20so%20and%20so%20was%20heroic%20and%20so%20on%20%E2%80%93%20I%20was%20there.%20You%20must%20have%20been%20there%2C%20watching%20this.%20Very%20few%20put%20up%20any%20kind%20of%20resistance%2C%20other%20than%20the%20small%20underground%20publications.%20A%20similar%20thing%20is%20happening%20now%2C%20but%20the%20difference%20is%2C%20that%20I%20still%20have%20hope%20%E2%80%93%20there%20are%20spaces%20and%20the%20new%20technology%20and%20platforms%20are%20giving%20us%20opportunities%20for%20voices%20to%20be%20raised%20in%20defense%20of%20democratic%20rights%2C%20freedoms%20and%20things%20like%20this.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20easy%20to%20come%20to%20an%20answer%2C%20because%20on%20the%20one%20hand%20I%E2%80%99m%20against%20hate%20and%20communalism%2C%20but%20how%20do%20you%20figure%20out%20ways%20of%20dealing%20with%20it%3F%20That%E2%80%99s%20what%20we%20are%20talking%20about%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20you%20know%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20very%20sad%20conclusion%20that%E2%80%99s%20suggested%20by%20what%20you%20said%20just%20now.%20The%20one%20quality%20one%20looks%20for%20in%20channel%20owners%2C%20in%20newspaper%20proprietors%2C%20is%20spine%20%E2%80%93%20the%20capacity%20to%20withstand%20political%20pressure%3B%20political%20pressure%20more%20than%20commercial%20pressure%20because%20that%20is%20the%20pressure%20that%20really%20hurts%2C%20and%20that%20is%20the%20one%20quality%20that%20seems%20to%20be%20missing%20for%20whatever%20reason.%20Whether%20they%20are%20personally%20vulnerable%20or%20whether%20they%20are%20liable%20to%20seek%20commercial%20solutions%20that%20bring%20easy%20money%2C%20the%20spine%20that%20is%20required%20t