rorist%20state%20that%20has%20brazenly%20engaged%20in%20extrajudicial%20killings%20not%20only%20on%20its%20own%20soil%2C%20but%20also%20on%20Canadian%20soil.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHarkirat%20Kaur%2C%20a%2019-year-old%20Sikh%20activist%2C%20on%20Monday%20said%20she%20was%20initially%20relieved%20to%20hear%20Trudeau%20say%20that%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9Ccredible%E2%80%9D%20intelligence%20linking%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20the%20shooting%20of%20Nijjar%2C%20the%3Cem%3E%20Vancouver%20Sun%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvancouversun.com%2Fnews%2Flocal-news%2Feby-deeply-disturbed-by-csis-briefing-on-nijjar-killing-in-surrey%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fcanada-accuses-indian-government-of-assassinating-sikh-citizen-in-vancouver-expels-senior-diplomat%5C%22%3EAfter%20Trudeau%20Alleges%20Indian%20Govt%20Link%20to%20Assassination%20of%20Sikh%20Citizen%2C%20India%2C%20Canada%20Expel%20Diplomats%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20relief%20soon%20turned%20to%20resentment%2C%20she%20said.%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20did%20it%20take%20so%20long%3F%20Why%20did%20it%20take%20someone%20to%20be%20killed%20for%20us%20to%20have%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20acknowledgment%20of%20what%20is%20happening%3F%E2%80%9D%20Kaur%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EVancouver%20Sun%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20saying.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoninder%20Singh%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20B.C.%20Sikh%20Gurdwara%20Council%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fcanada%2Fbritish-columbia%2Fbc-sikh-leader-killing-reaction-1.6970897%5C%22%3Etold%20CBC%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20reaction%20of%20the%20Sikh%20community%20was%20%E2%80%9Cmixed%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20Canada%20is%20actually%20declaring%20that%20India%20is%20an%20actual%20actor%20in%20this%2C%20I%20think%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20first%20step%