5C%22%3EWhat%20Is%20Sanatana%20Dharma%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20if%20ever%20they%20needed%20any%20ideological%20justification%20or%20support%20for%20their%20current%20demand%20for%20a%20nationwide%20caste%20census%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20better%20place%20to%20look%20than%20to%20what%20Bhagwat%20has%20said%C2%A0publicly%20in%20an%20address%20at%20Nagpur%2C%20the%20heart%C2%A0of%20Brahminical%20Hinduism.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20while%20laid-back%20academic%20remarks%20are%20afloat%2C%20the%20question%20to%20ask%20directly%20is%3A%20who%20are%20the%20%E2%80%9Cwe%E2%80%9D%20in%20Bhagwat%E2%80%99s%20statement%2C%20if%20not%20the%20%E2%80%98upper%E2%80%99%20caste%20twice%20born%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20could%20be%20a%20more%20simply%20and%20strongly%20expressed%20view%20as%20to%20how%20the%20social%20content%20of%20Sanatan%20Dharma%20has%20helped%20to%20constitute%20a%20%E2%80%9CBrahminical%20Hinduism%E2%80%9D%20which%20has%20through%20the%20ages%20alienated%20the%20majority%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9CBahujan%20Samaj%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWere%20one%20to%20read%20Kancha%20Ilaiah%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.goodreads.com%2Fen%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F1230699%5C%22%3EWhy%20I%20Am%20Not%20a%20Hindu%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eone%20would%20only%20find%20Bhagwat%E2%80%99s%20outburst%20against%20caste%20oppression%20laid%20out%20in%20greater%20detail%2C%20including%20how%20such%20%E2%80%9CBrahminical%20Hinduism%E2%80%9D%20has%20through%20those%202%2C000%20years%20that%20Bhagwat%20has%20referenced%20excommunicated%20the%20Shudra%20castes%20and%20outcasts%20not%20just%20socially%20but%20also%20in%20terms%20of%20their%20culturally%20discrete%20allegiance%20to%20a%20pantheon%20of%20deities%20away%20from%20the%20Brahminical%20triumvirate%20of%20Brahma%2C%20Vishnu%2C%20Mahesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20to%20the%20claim%20made%20for%20the%20eternal%C2%A0verity%20of%20Sanatan%20Dharma%2C%C2%A0the%20days%20to%20com