vileged-kids%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eonline%20education%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20was%20even%20recognised%20by%20the%20Organisation%20for%20Economic%20Co-operation%20and%20Development%20Education%20(OECD).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202020%2C%20the%20Directorate%20of%20School%20Education%20rolled%20out%20a%20tele%2Fonline%20education%20programme%20through%20which%20education%20was%20offered%20through%20TV%20(Doordarshan%2C%20Kohima)%20and%20radio%20(All%20India%20Radio%2C%20Kohima).%20In%20May%202020%2C%20they%20also%20offered%20educational%20content%20through%20a%20YouTube%20channel.%20This%20programme%20was%20led%20by%20C%20Shanavas%20%E2%80%94%20principal%20director%20of%20school%20education%20%E2%80%94%20and%20supported%20by%20Nellayapan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHeartiest%20congratulations%20to%20the%20awardees%20of%20Governor's%20Gold%20Medal%20and%20Governor's%20Commendation%20Certificate%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2F74th_IndependenceDay%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%2374th_IndependenceDay%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FqdEbUZl7OP%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FqdEbUZl7OP%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Neiphiu%20Rio%20(%40Neiphiu_Rio)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNeiphiu_Rio%2Fstatus%2F1294503464827944962%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2015%2C%202020%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20hilly%20areas%20in%20the%20state%20face%20network%20issues.%20So%20we%20ironed%20out%20a%20plan%20that%20would%20reach%20every%20student%2C%20irrespective%20of%20network.%20We%20were%20also%20the%20first%20state%20to%20conduct%20online%20exams%20for%20students%20from%20Classes%205%E2%80%9312%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nellayapan%2C%20who%20was%20awarded%20the%20Governor%E2%80%99s%20commendation%20certificate%20for%20his%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWorking%20with%20IAS%20officers%20like%20Shanavas%20was%20also%20a%20big%20motivation%20for%20Nellayapan.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20had%20the%20privilege%20of%20working%20with%20many%20IAS%20officers.%20They%20are%20an%20inspiration%20for%20me%20and%20I%20wish%20to%20work%20like%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20physics%20teacher.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERecognising%20his%20work%20and%20efforts%20towards%20improving%20education%20in%20the%20state%2C%20Nellayapan%20was%20made%20the%20OSD%20to%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20Nagaland%20in%20April%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20road%20to%20here%20has%20not%20been%20an%20easy%20one%20for%20him%2C%20he%20shares.%20He%20has%20had%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20his%20family%20for%20more%20than%20three%20decades.%20He%20credits%20his%20wife%20for%20being%20a%20big%20reason%20for%20his%20success.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20wife%20is%20my%20rock.%20She%20supported%20me%20since%20the%20day%20we%20got%20married.%20She%20also%20helped%20my%20younger%20sister%20get%20married.%20Today%2C%20my%20wife%20is%20a%20successful%20executive%20in%20the%20private%20sector%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Nellayapan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202006%2C%20his%20wife%20and%20children%20moved%20to%20Trivandrum%20because%20of%20his%20wife%E2%80%99s%20job.%20He%20proudly%20mentions%20that%20his%20son%20is%20now%20a%20doctor%2C%20and%20his%20daughter%20is%20in%20Class%2011.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReminiscing%20the%20past%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20concentrate%20only%20on%20work%20because%20I%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20responsibility%20when%20I%20came%20here.%20I%20had%20to%20ensure%20that%20my%20siblings%20studied%20well%20and%20my%20parents%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20borrow%20money.%20Poverty%20and%20responsibility%20guided%20me%20on%20the%20right%20path%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENellayapan%20has%20a%20message%20to%20all%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F306810%2Fthis-heartwarming-story-of-determination-and-resilience-started-with-a-simple-no%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyoung%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20substitute%20for%20hard%20work.%20You%20might%20get%20the%20reward%20late%2C%20but%20keep%20at%20it.%20Hustle%20for%20a%20better%20tomorrow%20with%20focus.%20You%20will%20be%20rewarded%20for%20your%20efforts.%20Just%20work%20hard%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20let%20your%20mind%20get%20diverted.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20the%20day%2C%20many%20people%20helped%20his%20father%20with%20the%20loans.%20Even%20though%20his%20parents%20don%E2%80%99t%20require%20his%20assistance%20now%2C%20this%20government%20officer%20is%20a%20strong%20believer%20in%20%3Cem%3Ekarma%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Today%2C%20he%20supports%20six%20students%20in%20their%20education.%20%E2%80%9CGod%20has%20blessed%20me%3B%20I%20have%20to%20pass%20on%20the%20help%20to%20those%20who%20need%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oecd-ilibrary.org%2Fsites%2F61d5c87b-en%2Findex.html%3FitemId%3D%2Fcontent%2Fcomponent%2F61d5c87b-en%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EOECD%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695101867000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FNellayapan-1695049811.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D330237%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nellayapan%20B%2C%20Officer%20on%20Special%20Duty%20(OSD)%20to%20the%20Nagaland%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20grew%20up%20in%20crushing%20poverty%20in%20a%20one-room%20house%20in%20a%20village%20in%20Kanniyakumari.%20Exemplifying%20the%20power%20of%20education%2C%20his%20inspirin