ther%20added%20them%20as%20our%20family%20grew.%20The%20garages%20were%20acting%20as%20a%20wall%20between%20the%20greenery%20and%20the%20plantation.%20I%20decided%20to%20pull%20it%20down%20and%20make%20it%20an%20open%20patio%20space%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%20adding%20that%20this%20was%20the%20only%20major%20change%20she%20has%20done%20to%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUpon%20entering%20the%20house%2C%20you%20will%20be%20greeted%20by%20a%20lavish%20dining%20area%20made%20by%20restructuring%20two%20smaller%20rooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20my%20learning%20came%20from%20the%20building%20itself.%20I%20did%20not%20have%20to%20refer%20to%20any%20other%20properties%20for%20the%20design%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20house%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20windows%20that%20flood%20light%20in%3B%20my%20father%20never%20used%20bulbs%20and%20lights%20during%20the%20day.%20I%20wanted%20to%20keep%20that%20intact.%20I%20added%20a%20few%20more%20windows%20to%20utilise%20the%20sun%20to%20the%20fullest%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20also%20has%20a%20very%20strong%20foundation%20with%20mortar%20bricks.%20I%20did%20not%20want%20to%20touch%20them%20as%20they%20were%20the%20foundation%20of%20the%20building%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhenever%20I%20saw%20the%20house%2C%20I%20always%20thought%20about%20how%20many%20man-hours%20must%20have%20gone%20into%20making%20it%20100%20years%20ago.%20The%20skill%20and%20masonry%20must%20be%20preserved%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20when%20I%20decided%20to%20pull%20down%20the%20garage%2C%20I%20used%20manual%20labour%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Anupa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-2-1694786653.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20house%20has%20several%20windows%20to%20utilise%20the%20wind%20and%20keep%20the%20house%20cool%20naturally.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-2-1694786653.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-2-1694786653-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-2-1694786653-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-2-1694786653-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-2-1694786653-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330102%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20house%20has%20several%20windows%20to%20utilise%20the%20wind%20and%20keep%20the%20house%20cool%20naturally.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Anupa%20Kurian%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20would%20have%20taken%20a%20JCB%20just%20minutes%20to%20break%20the%20place%20down%2C%20but%20all%20the%20bricks%20would%20have%20gone%20to%20waste.%20Because%20of%20using%20manual%20labour%20instead%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20use%20those%20bricks%20in%20constructing%20some%20of%20the%20extensions%20in%20my%20room%20and%20the%20patio%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20my%20father%20was%20against%20removing%20the%20garage%20and%20constructing%20a%20patio%2C%20presently%20he%20is%20the%20one%20who%20uses%20it%20the%20most!%E2%80%9D%20she%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20example%20where%20Anupa%20chose%20to%20keep%20the%20originality%20of%20the%20house%20is%20with%20the%20roof%20rafters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20house%20was%20built%20using%20wooden%20rafters%20and%20most%20of%20the%20people%20advised%20us%20to%20change%20it%20to%20steel.%20However%2C%20on%20inspection%2C%20I%20found%20that%20the%20roof%20was%20stronger%20than%20ever.%20I%20decided%20to%20go%20against%2