oing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F54545%2Fwomen-farmers-empowerment-fighting-maharashtra-drought%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epoultry%20farming%20%3C%2Fa%3Efor%20the%20past%20four%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20shares%20that%20he%20now%20earns%20up%20to%20Rs%2060%2C000%20per%20day%20through%20this%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESharing%20learnings%20with%20new%20IAS%20officers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Ravindra%20advanced%20his%20farm%20with%20improved%20technologies%20like%20indoor%20vertical%20farming%2C%20greenhouse%20farming%2C%20automatic%20watering%2C%20drip%20systems%2C%20remote%20sensing%20irrigation%20systems%2C%20and%20organic%20farming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20employed%20only%2050%20workers%20to%20manage%20my%20poultry%20farm%20spread%20across%2050%20acres.%20Most%20of%20the%20work%20is%20automated.%20For%20example%2C%20from%20collecting%20eggs%20from%20broilers%20and%20giving%20feed%20to%20poultry%20birds%2C%20to%20collecting%20their%20excreta%2C%20everything%20is%20ensured%20using%20machines%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20in%202013%2C%20he%20was%20selected%20by%20the%20state%20government%20as%20one%20of%20the%2080%20progressive%20farmers%20to%20be%20sent%20to%20Europe%20for%20a%2010-day%20trip%20to%20understand%20the%20nitty-gritty%20of%20expanding%20the%20farming%20business%20with%20machinery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Famravati-1694610755.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%202022%2C%20Ravindra%20was%20also%20conferred%20with%20the%20prestigious%20Jagjivan%20Ram%20Abhinav%20Kisan%20Puraskar%20by%20the%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Agricultural%20Research%20(ICAR).%5C%2